  "detailed_description": "<strong>Always dreamed of becoming a forklift operator? Now you can!</strong><br>You get to drive a forklift, move pallets around and do crazy stunts.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/498570/extras/dfc71c274622805542fd9ad96ae9edf8.avif?t=1667052237\" width=600 height=254 /></span><br><br>Features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> The forklifting adventure you've always been dreaming of!<br></li><li> Experience the glamorous life of a warehouse worker.<br></li><li> Realistic, accurate and highly responsive controls.<br></li><li> Support for most steering wheels.<br></li><li> All the pallets you can wish for!<br></li><li> Pick pallets up!<br></li><li> Put pallets down!</li></ul><br>The game you never knew you wanted!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/498570/extras/eaa7d9a517e27bb2b8f6c83fc8c02f84.avif?t=1667052237\" width=600 height=254 /></span><br><br><br>Force feedback only works on Windows, and may not work on racing wheels.<br>The Steam controller is emulated as an Xbox360 controller.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/498570/extras/e300bc04e65fe0f873788649656cf4b6.avif?t=1667052237\" width=600 height=254 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Always dreamed of becoming a forklift operator? Now you can!</strong><br>You get to drive a forklift, move pallets around and do crazy stunts.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/498570/extras/dfc71c274622805542fd9ad96ae9edf8.avif?t=1667052237\" width=600 height=254 /></span><br><br>Features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> The forklifting adventure you've always been dreaming of!<br></li><li> Experience the glamorous life of a warehouse worker.<br></li><li> Realistic, accurate and highly responsive controls.<br></li><li> Support for most steering wheels.<br></li><li> All the pallets you can wish for!<br></li><li> Pick pallets up!<br></li><li> Put pallets down!</li></ul><br>The game you never knew you wanted!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/498570/extras/eaa7d9a517e27bb2b8f6c83fc8c02f84.avif?t=1667052237\" width=600 height=254 /></span><br><br><br>Force feedback only works on Windows, and may not work on racing wheels.<br>The Steam controller is emulated as an Xbox360 controller.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/498570/extras/e300bc04e65fe0f873788649656cf4b6.avif?t=1667052237\" width=600 height=254 /></span>",
